                                27.0895 26.5971 27.8799 26.9787C28.6702 27.3604 29.5362 27.5594 30.4139 27.5612H32.4822C33.7759 27.5612 35.0167 27.0472 35.9315 26.1324C36.8463 25.2176 37.3602
